{"title":"大旗","authors":["任惠敏"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":10,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任惠敏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我出生在那面鲜红的大旗下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举旗的是我父亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了保护她在天下飘扬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲的胸脯落满子弹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他捂住喷涌的一个个洞穴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如战马嘶鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临终围着主人久久地亲近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我渐渐长大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带上红领巾就想到大旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿上红裙子就想到大旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见红窗帘就想到大旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大旗一如既往在蓝天下飘舞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将父亲的墓地映得火红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想走进去告诉他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那旗早已长成林子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜甜地自由自在地飞扬……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我模模糊糊看到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他还是那个姿势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身上的洞穴结满了鸡冠花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我对父亲的怀念从大旗下长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大旗越升越高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的怀念越来越深"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}